1- laravel new "nome"
2- npm install
3- npm i admin-lte@v3.0.0-alpha.2 --save
4- config .env
5- criação do BD
6- php artisan make:auth
7- php artisan migrate
8- criação do arq 'master.blade.php'
9- copiar o código de "adminlte.io/themes/dev/AdminLTE/starter.html" 
   p/ 'master.blade.php'
10- substituir os links "js" por '<scrpt src="/js/app.js"><script>'
11- substituir os links css por '<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css">'
12- Mudar o @extends da pág home por "@extends('layout.master')"
13- Adicionar "require('admin-lte')" no arq "bootstrap.js"
14- Adicionar "@import '~admin-lte/dist/css/adminlte.css'" no arq "app.scss"
15- npm run watch
16- npm i @fortawesome/fontawesome-free
17- Adicionar '$fa-font-path: "../webfonts";' em "app.scss"
18- Adicionar em app.scss:
      @import "~@fortawesome/fontawesome-free/scss/fontawesome.scss"
      @import "~@fortawesome/fontawesome-free/scss/solid.scss"
      @import "~@fortawesome/fontawesome-free/scss/brands.scss"
19- Config vue-router: "npm i vue-router"
20- Importe do vue-router no arquivo "resources/js/app.js":
    import VueRouter from 'vue-router'
    Vue.use(VueRouter);
21- Instação do axios e vform: npm i axios vform
22- Criação do API/UserController: php artisan make:controller API/UserController --api      
23- Ajustar a data: npm i moment --save
24- Vue Progress Bar: npm i vue-progressbar --save
25- Sweetalert2: npm i sweetalert2 --save
26- instalando passport: https://laravel.com/docs/5.8/passport
27- instalação intervention image: 
    - composer require intervention/image
    - http://image.intervention.io/getting_started/installation#laravel

 